CONVENIENT
Connections AT SEATTLE
TO AND FROM ALASKA
Alaska Airlines Golden Nugget schedule permits same day all jet travel to the
Last Frontier. Northbound passengers from California, the Midwest
and the East Coast can fly to Seattle, transfer to the Golden Nugget Jet
and be in Alaska by 6:50 p.m. "Going out," as Alaskans say, the Golden
Nugget Jet provides the same quick and convenient
connections with jet flights South and East.
